modName: Tattoos for UNP UNPB body-Optional Freckles and Tanlines for Barbarian Skin
summary: Tattoos for all body parts. For 1dot51 UNP body and HoneyVanity\'s Barbarian skin with/without tanlines, and optional Freckles
descriptionHtml:
READ THE CHANGELOG AND THE DESCRIPTION! Files section is messy, choose well. 
THERE IS DARKER/BRIGHTER TANLINES IN THE OPTIONAL SECTION! (If the normal doesn\'t look good with your enb/graphic settings)
 I uploaded the tattoos PSD for 4k use, some of the tats are low-res...i can\'t do miracle with them....you will see.

No more updates for this mod, actually i never modified the tats after release, only the skins. If I do tanlines for other skins, those will be in another mod.

[heading]Description[/heading]
For user request I uploaded my tattoos here. Its compatible with the UNP and UNPB [i](works for me)[/i] body. You can use it with any Map [i](the tanlined version works best what i mentioned in the More info section...still...not necessary)[/i]

Advise: Use this: Sub Surface Full Body Map for Coverwomen and UNP UNPB Bodies by MrTroubleMaker -http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30050   Its just the best.

I UPLOADED my stripped down PSD in the MISCELLANEOUS for personal use. Made for 2048x2048 body textures. You need only Photoshop/GIMP and the DDS plugin for it, really, no skill needed.  I don\'t have too. Try it. It will pay off.  
Except the back tat all of them are free to use what I found on the web or made by myself.

If you want the Barbarian Skin without Tats, check my other mod [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30034/]here[/url]
[line]
FEATURES
THESE FILES ARE UNCOMPRESSED! (Body~20Mb)

-Barbarian Skin Features- Original from HoneyVanity [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24318]here[/url]
- Brighter and Less Bright tanlines in the optional files...
- Freckled/Hairy options of Tanned 2048x2048 body textures.
- Freckled/Hairy options of the Original 2048x2048 body textures.
- Matching face texture - Freckled/Non-freckled (You don\'t HAVE to use it, but for best results I highly recommend it.)
- Optional Face Texture - Freckled/Non-freckled (Should be no neck line here too. it has color mismatch, i already fixed it, i will upload with other things later)
     *I ADVISE TO CHECK OUT HoneyVanity\'s ORIGINAL MOD FIRST*

-1dot51 Skin Features-
- DOWNSCALED to 2048x2048
- Freckled options
- Hairy options
- No Face texture (I cannot port the freckles for every damn facetexture, you have to use the Photoshop/GIMP - individual PSD uploaded for that. or from here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/15766 )

[heading]INSTALLATION[/heading]
There is only manual install. Please Back up your files before using this.

1. Extract to the Game\'s folder and overwrite.
2. Enjoy

Using a Custom Race (probably you do): If you use a custom race, overwrite the textures in the custom race directory. Texture paths change from race to race, check their zips to find where are their textures.

[heading]MORE INFO[/heading]

How to look like on the pics:
[list]
[*]Maps and sk maps from: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21387]Maori Body Tattoo and tanlines UNPB Version 2 by kruaka27[/url] (I didn\'t check where he get those, maybe his work, maybe not, but they look pretty good.)
[*]Textures: Barbarian skin with Tanlines +Freckles with the Optional face.
[*]Sweaty spectacular maps from: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/28946]Sporty Sexy Sweat - wet body skin texture - CBBE UNP UNPB [*]ADEC Vanilla by Xs2reality[/url]
[*]Skeleton for the same curves: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26800]XP32 Maximum Skeleton -XPMS by xp32 [/url] (absolutley not necessary, but good)
[*]Face: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/7897]envision Face by DD AKT[/url] with larger lips.
[/list]
With a tiny work you can make your char almost look like mine. I can provide any more help in that individually.


----Other Questions-----

Clothes on the Pictures:
 -  On the second pic: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/27758]Beads Bikini UNP by japantarou Fixed and UNPB also BBP BBPx by MrTroubleMaker[/url]
 -  First: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21271]Bouncy Bodices and Booties for UNPB and UNP both with and without BBP by dikr[/url]

Can i learn what lightning/enb/fxaa etc. mods you are using?
 -  Ofc, [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/20781]Project ENB by Bronze316[/url],
 -  [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/17802]Project Reality - Climates Of Tamriel - Weather - Lighting by JJC71[/url], 
 -  [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/27043]Enhanced Lights and FX by anamorfus[/url]

What are my future plans with this mod? [i](note for myself too, before i forget them...)[/i]
- Porting: Not Really. If you ask that, i will show you instead how you can do that yourself. Takes 15 mins with all the stuff. And you will be able to make/customize tattoos too.
- One day i will do tanlines for other skins. I\'m an idiot and i modified the textures itself. Well, personally i think it looks better. Not perfect tho. But with my limited photoshop skill i can\'t port it, i can only make a new.

---- Bugs, Errors -------
I don\'t know any...yet. If you found any bugs, errors in the files or in the page, inform me. I\'m a very silly person, usually forgetting elementary things

---- Changelog -------
FINAL
[list]
[*]4K Tats and Freckles PSD uploaded. Can\'t do miracle with low-res tats, but....it\'s something  
[*]RESOURCE PSD updated with the fixed skin.  
[*]Tan fix: Left and Right breast tans are now identical.  
UPDATE V1.5
[*]Custom Head now have better color matching. the the neck color on the body and the head are IDENTICAL.
[*]RESOURCE PSDs updated.
[*]Less Bright tan options uploaded.
[*]Brighter tan options uploaded.
[*]Body map and subsurface map like on my char. kuraka27\'s
UPDATE V1.4
[*]Wrong Hair placing on the Tanlined versions. fixed.
UPDATE V1.3
[*]Barbarian tanlines edit: Darker. [i](still looks like shit on full pale game option...not a surprise)[/i] it was indeed too bright.
[*]Panty tans edit, I like it this way. [i](5th time redone...I needed a beer for that)[/i]
[*]Resouce PSD updated.
UPDATE V1.2
[*]Thanks to Rost3, he let me use his freckle texture - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/15766
[*]Reuploaded everything + uploaded the Freckled skins
[*]Barbarian panty tans redone, now everything look much better.
UPDATE V1.1
[*] There was a Map<->Texture mismatch on the barbarian skins. Fixed.
[*] Some Detail improvement on the barbarian skins [i](down there)[/i]
[*] Updated Resource PSD uploaded.
UPDATE V1
[*]Barbarian Skin with proper head and hand textures uploaded. Hairy and Hairless version.
[*]PSD Updated - use it with respect. Not for me, for those who let me use the things inside it.
[/list]

---- Contact ----
You have questions? Fell free to PM me!


That\'s all folks for now. Have fun!
[heading]CREDITS[/heading]
With full admire, I used his body for an asset:
Dimon99 - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709
Ful credit goes to *AbigailLarson for the Perfect Back tattoo - http://mirrorcradle.deviantart.com/art/Commission-Grave-Robin-173061740
Special Thanks to *HoneyVanity who let me to use that amazing Barbarian Skin! - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24318
Thanks to *Rost3\'s for the amazing freckle texture - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/15766
Thank you to *kruaka27 who let me upload his body map and sk map as an asset. Amazing Tanlines and Tats by the way, he is the reason why i started this - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21387
